description: This super green baked eggs dish is a delicious way to get veggies into your breakfast.
keywords: Baked eggs,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Gluten free,Egg,Lemon,Sesame free,Halal,Soy free,Wheat free,Vegetarian,Kale,Dairy free
name: Kale & Brussels Sprout Baked Eggs Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the oil in a large, deep non-stick frying pan on medium heat and cook the spring onions, shredded sprouts and kale for 5-6 minutes to soften. Add the chilli and garam masala and cook for 1 minute. Stir in the lemon juice and a pinch of zest.
Create 8 gaps in the pan and crack in the eggs. Cook for 5-7 minutes until just set and serve.
